highlights.text: MXZI has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “MONTAGEM TOMADA - Slowed” is the highest at #22.
“Cry For Me” by Michita and 愛海 has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 122 days straight.
“Anh Đã Chờ Rất Lâu” by Sixkie Dawgz is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #4.
“รักแรกพบ (Knock Knock) - From ซองแดงแต่งผี” by Billkin is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 25 spots at #51.
